title: [CLIENT] [QUEUE] Can not queue. Find Match button does not work.
body:
Hello,

Ranked Queue was not available earlier so I queued Normal approximately 2 hours ago.

After countdown it froze on zero seconds - no launch - players could still chat. Eventually all players left.

Now when I try queue any game mode, I can select "Find Match" but it clicks and does not enter queue.

Of note: Custom/Practice etc says I am already in a game.

I can not log into support to submit a ticket, website returns error try again later.

Cheers.

replies.body: yea they noticed and they said they trying to sort it out now i been waiting for 3 hours was stuck in champ select norm blind pick

Agent Mindstar (OCE)  - 3 minutes ago 2 of 2 Rioter Comments
Hi folks - just an update here.

There was an incident on the OCE server earlier this morning (which lines up with when you got initially stuck in games / champ select). This left some players in "ghost games", where different parts of the server think you are in a game, when you are not.

Unfortunately, there's no way for us to re-sync this information without restarting the entire OCE platform. It will eventually self-resolve, once those games expire, which in normal circumstances should take approximately 3 hours.

TL;DR - it should be fixed for each of you within the next hour.
